description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 47, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 94, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Nine Lives for South, and 2 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [94 Votes, Common]
